name: Learn to swim, learn to swim, learn to swim
description:
i guess if you live in a desert and dream of going to the beach need to learn how to swim from that device showing how, have to pick several channels to see which ones seem logical or true...  

*******  
from mind's own desert, getting some water from a magical source, a device that is like a toolshed but seems to be responding to my mind's thirst for knowing, not available in this desert i am inside of, it may or may not be real. heart is picking pathways to various kinds of communal consciousness, sorting friends, allegiances, frienemies and enemies, purging or feeding on what to drink.  
 

 *** ________ ......   ______ 
Learn to swim, learn to swim, learn to swim
'Cause Mom's gonna fix it all soon
Mom's comin' 'round to put it back the way it ought to be
Learn to swim, learn to swim

Learn to swim, learn to swim
